<p id="FlK8kP">Overall, the Spectre x360 13 hits the right balance of features, performance, design, and cost better than any other laptop option right now, earning it our recommendation.</p>
<h1 id="G99For">The Mac option: Apple MacBook Pro 13 (two USB-C ports)</h1>
<div class="c-wide-block">  <figure class="e-image">
  <span class="e-image__inner">
    
    <span class="e-image__image " data-original="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/18311683/akrales_190711_3536_0049.jpg">
      
